msgstr "支持的功能"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/spring-cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus provides compatibility with the following Spring Cache annotations:"
msgstr "Quarkus 支持以下 Spring Cache 注解："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/spring-cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`@Cacheable`"
msgstr "`@Cacheable`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/spring-cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`@CachePut`"
msgstr "`@CachePut`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/spring-cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`@CacheEvict`"
msgstr "`@CacheEvict`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/spring-cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Note that in this first version of the Spring Cache annotations extension, not all features of these annotations are supported\n"
"(with proper errors being logged when trying to use an unsupported feature).\n"
"However, additional features are planned for future releases."
msgstr "请注意，在 Spring Cache 注解扩展的此首个版本中，并非支持这些注解的所有功能（尝试使用未支持的功能时，系统会记录相应的错误信息）。不过，计划在未来版本中增加更多功能。"

